reviewText:
If you're looking for a silly movie to riff with friends, look no further than Winky the Little Bear. (a.k.a. The Countryside Bears) It's weird, it's funny for all the wrong reasons, and it's Dingo Pictures at it's most meh.
But if you're a parent looking for something to entertain your kids, this isn't the DVD for you.

(P.S. There is no character at all in this movie named Winky.)

I bought this DVD and it didn't had the bonus cartoons in it. It's just the crappy cartoon itself. It's better known as Countryside Bears in Europe. Dingo Picture movies here in the good ol' US, well I'd never!
